# Volkern Properties - Platform Deployment

## Environment Variables for Vercel

To deploy successfully to Vercel, you need to configure the following environment variables:

### NextAuth configuration
NEXTAUTH_URL="https://your-domain.vercel.app"
NEXTAUTH_SECRET="your-secret-key-at-least-32-chars"

### CRM MCP Integration
VOLKERN_MCP_URL="https://your-mcp-server-endpoint.com/api"
VOLKERN_MCP_API_KEY="your-mcp-api-key"

### Database (If using Phase 5 Features)
DATABASE_URL="your-postgresql-url"

## Local Setup
1. Clone the repository
2. Run `npm install`
3. Create a `.env` file based on this template
4. Run `npm run dev`
